        {'instr':'', 'prompt':'Using the Bed Occupancy, Department P&L, AND Patient Volume Tracker sheets in HC_01_Hospital_Operations.xlsx, prepare a RAG decision table that separates immediate operating risks from strategic choices. Highlight where hospitals and departments are already Red, where the evidence is Amber but trending worse, and where Green items can be left to normal cadence.'},
        {'instr':'', 'prompt':'Using the OT Utilisation, Patient Volume Tracker, AND JCI Compliance Score sheets in HC_01_Hospital_Operations.xlsx, draft the questions you would ask in the next executive review. Present them as a RAG table with columns for Question, Evidence, Why It Matters, Decision Needed, and Follow-up Owner.'}
