        {'instr':'', 'prompt':'Open PH_01_Drug_Portfolio.xlsx in Excel for Web. Using Copilot in Excel, pull data from THREE tabs simultaneously — Product Revenue, Market Share Analysis AND Regulatory Approval Log — and build a new sheet called \'8-Week Supply Watchlist\'. Create an eight-week watchlist with KPI tiles, a line chart with a secondary axis for the pressure metric, a second chart showing count of Red items by week, sparklines for each leading indicator, and conditional formatting Red/Amber/Green based on trend deterioration.'}
